    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2009-04-23</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2009-05-12T12:51:43Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Long-Term Care Affordability and Security Act of 2009 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) include long-term care insurance as a benefit under tax-exempt employee benefit cafeteria plans and flexible spending arrangements; and (2) extend certain consumer protections under the long-term care insurance model regulation promulgated by the National Association of Insurance Commissioners to all contracts for long-term care insurance.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
